item.dc:creator: @usman555 usman555
item.description:
@usman555 wrote:

  add this to your code when you click the ItemID
        [code]
        setAnimation(1500);
        playerSE = 1501;
        playerSEW = 1851;
        playerSER = 1851;
        playerSEA = 1851;
        playerEnergy = 99;
        playerLevel[3] = 99;
        sendFrame126(playerEnergy + "%", 149);
        updateRequired = true;
        appearanceUpdateRequired = true;[/code]
